<div class="title">Snort, Eat, and Smoked</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Weebl&Exact=1">Weebl</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Weebl. "Snort, Eat, and Smoked: An Experience with Caffeine (exp30916)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 16, 2004. erowid.org/exp/30916</div>

<br/>



